title: United Kingdom Imports of Live Trees & Plants
description: Imports of Live Trees & Plants in the United Kingdom increased to 105.74 GBP Million in September from 101.30 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Live Trees & Plants in the United Kingdom averaged 83.67 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 179.44 GBP Million in March of 2021 and a record low of 37.99 GBP Million in July of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Live Trees & Plants.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
